Directed by Imran Khan. Imran Khan. Cast . Manoj Baksh. Priya Choudhur. Mohit Gandh. Ranbeeir Kals. Om Kapoo. Zulfi Rajpu. Disha Sachdev. Inderpal Sing. Produced by. Dev Saluja

Cast Manoj Bakshi (Father). Priya Choudhury (Priya).Mohit Gandhi. Ranbeeir Kalsi (Mandy). Om Kapoor (Son of Ekta Nanda). Zulfi Rajput (Reporter reporting on demonetisation). Disha Sachdeva (Soniya). Inderpal Singh (Inder)

Languages Hindi

Producers Dev Saluja. Film Editing by. JD Singh. Visual Effects by. Vimal Kumawat. Editorial Department. Vimal Kumawat. Additional Crew. Aniiket Limje.

Production Kreative Krishna entertainment
